lth and well-being.\n<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\n  For Dr., the Neymar Jr. It is a serious project that is transforming lives. \u201cI&#8217;m super impressed with you guys, congratulations! You come to Instituto Neymar to learn, you have many opportunities here and, because of this opportunity, there are no limits for you. Make your dreams come true, because they have no limit. With ethics, family values \u200b\u200band humility you will find success\u201d, he says.\n<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" onerror=\"this.src='https:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/image-not-available.jpg'\" src=\"http:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/word-image-13232-2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-13234\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/word-image-13232-2.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/word-image-13232-2-300x200.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/word-image-13232-2-768x512.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>\n  Foto: Instituto Neymar Jr.\n<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\n  According to the Administrative Director of the INJR, Jos\u00e9 Ben\u00edcio da Silva Santos, receiving partners who share the same values \u200b\u200bas the Institute is always synonymous with gratitude. \u201cThe purposes that we always propagate, when they are absorbed by the partners who arrive here and visit and understand this whole process, first of creation, then of execution, we are very happy\u201d, he says.\n<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"684\" onerror=\"this.src='https:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/image-not-available.jpg'\" src=\"http:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/word-image-13232-3.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-13235\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/word-image-13232-3.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/word-image-13232-3-300x200.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/word-image-13232-3-768x513.jpeg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>\n  Foto: Instituto Neymar Jr.\n<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><a id=\"post-13232-_m9h59485d6hk\"><\/a><strong>ABOUT ALIGNMED<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>\n  Alignmed Brasil is a technology and lifestyle company designed, researched and developed with a renowned group of doctors and sports scientists. The company uses science and technology for exoskeletal garments with an anatomical matrix of bands, panels and seams, collectively called NeuroBands\u00ae.\n<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\n  NeuroBands technology can be used to retrain inappropriate postures due to habitual movement behaviors caused by prolonged and repetitive motion sessions such as cell phone, computer, electronics or sports injury. The technology is supported by unprecedented research of clinical experience in more than 200,000 people to date who have used the products.\n<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>This Tuesday (18), the Instituto Neymar Jr. received a visit from Dr. Gregory Markarian, CEO of Alignmed Brasil, a technology company operating in the sports and health market. A partner of INJR since December 2021, Alignmed is present in the routine of the young people served because it believes in the social work carried out [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":13233,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[10],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.institutoneymarjr.org.br\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13232"}],"collecti